headline: Insurance and Taxes Now Cost More Than Mortgages for Many Homeowners
summary: Insurers have pushed big rate increases because of losses from natural disasters and rising costs to repair homes.  Surging home values in recent years, meanwhile, have lifted property taxes for many homeowners.
